title: Does Jared Kouchner's brother have a company that took part in the COVID-19 test?
subtitle: Oscar, a digital health insurance company that recently established a user service to find COVID-19 testing centres, was co-founded by Joshua Kouchner.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: Jared Kouchner ' s brother, Joshua Kouchner, owns a company that operates on a COVID-19 test.
